{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8340953f2e","title":"中央文革关于进一步批判大毒草《刘少奇访问印度尼西亚》的通知","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5650ca95a8","index":0,"year":1968,"month":11,"day":18,"articleId":"8340953f2e"}],"tags":[{"id":"268718f23b","name":"新闻广播和出版","type":"主题"},{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"91736a0628","name":"中共中央通知","type":"发行机构"},{"id":"ed8d454915","name":"刘少奇","type":"主题"},{"id":"ef6e778547","name":"中央文件","type":"文稿大类"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f88934a640","type":"title","text":"中央文革关于进一步批判大毒草《刘少奇访问印度尼西亚》的通知","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"8340953f2e"},{"id":"b06b37614e","type":"paragraph","text":"各省、市、自治区革命委员会：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"8340953f2e"},{"id":"f5f8689e6b","type":"paragraph","text":"当前全国正处在揭发、控诉、批判刘贼叛党卖国滔天罪行的高潮中。为了配合大批判，各地可有领导地重新放映刘贼《访问印度尼西亚》（不登广告），并组织群众性的大批判，报上也可发表批判文章。我们即将再印制一批拷贝送发各地。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"8340953f2e"},{"id":"8b70d845e2","type":"paragraph","text":"中央文革","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"8340953f2e"},{"id":"340b528835","type":"paragraph","text":"一九六八年十一月十八日","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"8340953f2e"}],"page":{"id":"dd46a1494c","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"8340953f2e","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}